imdb.plot outline: The Health Warriors Network was created by Avatar Media as an interactive digital media platform for aboriginal youth in Alberta to learn more about health careers. The "Digital Stories" component of this project currently consists of 6 different videos each showcasing a young aboriginal youth and their stories as they work towards a career in a specific health related field.
